<p><b>php站内搜索：多关键字，加亮显示</b><hr>1.sql语句中的模糊查找<br><br>LIKE 条件一般用在指定搜索某字段的时候，通过"%_"通配符的作用实现模糊查找功能，通配符可以在前面也可以在后面或前后都有<br><br>搜索以mingzi开头的：select * from table where title like 'mingzi%';<br>搜索以mingzi结束的：select * from table where title like '%mingzi';<br>  搜索包含mingzi的：select * from table where title like '%mingzi%';<br><br>%表示0个或多个字符构成的字符串<br>_表示单个字符<br><hr></p><div align="center">	<form action=""method="post">		关键字：		<input type="text" name = "key"/>		<input type="submit" value="查询"/>	</form></div><table width=1000 border="0" align="center" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="1" bgcolor="#add3ef">	<?		$conn = @ mysql_connect("localhost", "root", "") or die("数据库链接错误");		mysql_select_db("bbs", $conn);		mysql_query("set names 'GBK'"); //使用GBK中文编码;			if($_POST['key'])		{			$key=$_POST['key'];						$key=explode(" ",$key);						$sql = "select * from message where title like '%".$key[0]."%' or title like '%".$key[1]."%'";			$query = mysql_query($sql);		}		$count=0;		$color="#eff3ff";		while($array=mysql_fetch_array($query))		{			$array=preg_replace("/($key[0])/i", "<font color=red><b>\\1</b></font>", $array);			$array=preg_replace("/($key[1])/i", "<font color=red><b>\\1</b></font>", $array);			if($count%2) {$color="#ffffff";}			else {$color="#eff3ff";}	?>	<tr bgcolor=<?=$color?>>		<td>标题：<?=$array['title']?></td>		<td>用户：<?=$array['user']?></td>		<td>内容：<?=$array['content']?></td>	</tr>	<?			$count++;		}	?></table><div align="center">	<b>共 <?=$count?> 条结果</b></div>